// TestRegression demonstrates the multi-device U2F authentication bug.
//
// BUG DESCRIPTION:
// When a user registers multiple U2F hardware tokens with Teleport, the
// authentication flow only presents a challenge for a single device, even
// though multiple devices are registered.
